# Bundled runtime resources are staged here at release time.
#
# psmux.exe (the native Windows tmux — https://github.com/psmux/psmux) is
# fetched by scripts/fetch-psmux.ps1 before a Windows `tauri build` and is
# gitignored (never committed — it's a ~2 MB binary, regenerated per release).
# The tauri.conf `bundle.resources` glob ("resources/*") packages whatever lands
# here; at runtime pty.rs::mux_bin resolves <resource_dir>/resources/psmux.exe
# as the fallback when no psmux/tmux is found on PATH.
